title: [Question] Can I use temporary id card to attend 2nd round jee counselling tmrw?
content: I have already attended round 1 and booked seat, coming tmrw for upgradation. Should I carry my rank card printout again or is the temporary id card they issued enough?

comments.body: Hi, the temporary ID card ID not necessary but you need to carry rank card and stuff, lol I am already here in the audi
